public class ExecuteJameleonScriptTag
extends JUnitFunctionTag

Used to acceptance test Jameleon tags. Executes a Jameleon script and checks various outputs.

reverseTestCaseCount

private void reverseTestCaseCount()
Rolls back the test case execution count. We do this so that the test case inside the script being run does not increment in the total # runs in the case it is data-driven. Basically, one script equals one test case run.
